You shouldn&#39;t be using two separate cells for this. You want `Activate`/`Deactivate` to appear in the same cell. So instead of using `hidden` on the `mat-cell`, use `ngIf` on the anchor tags to conditionally show `Activate`/`Deactivate`.
```html
